<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi, <%= @requestee.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have received a feedback request from <%= @requestor.first_last %> for
      your recent interaction (<%= @request.interaction.interaction_title %>) on
      <%= @request.interaction.interaction_date %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      To complete feedback for this request, you can use the following link: </br>
      <%= @feedback_link %>.
    </p>
    <p>Best,</p>
    <p>Rocking Chair Team</p>
  </body>
</html>